flowchart TD
    S0[draft] --> S1{duplicate detected}
    S1 -->|yes| S2[duplicate_review]
    S1 -->|no| S3[processing]

    S2 -->|continue| S3
    S2 -->|skip| S9[closed]

    S3 --> S4{extraction result}
    S4 -->|success| S5[ready]
    S4 -->|failed| S6[manual_required]
    S6 -->|manual markdown submitted| S5

    S5 --> S7[generating]
    S7 --> S8{generation result}
    S8 -->|success| S10[review_ready]
    S8 -->|provider/schema failure| S11[generation_failed]
    S11 -->|retry allowed| S7
    S11 -->|manual fallback| S6

    S10 --> S12[approved]
    S12 --> S13{publish path}
    S13 -->|connector publish success| S14[published]
    S13 -->|manual submission update| S15[submitted]

    S14 --> S9
    S15 --> S9
